# Getting Started with Cubase 15 Research Framework

This guide walks you through the initial setup of the Cubase Intelligence Framework for offline research and educational analysis.

## Prerequisites

- Valid Steinberg Cubase Pro 15 license  
- Windows 10/11 or macOS Sonoma+  
- Basic familiarity with Lua scripting

⚠️ This framework is for offline, private session research only. Do not use in collaborative or cloud-enabled projects.

Next Steps
Explore /examples/ for advanced automation templates
Review API_REFERENCE.md for object model documentation
Consult ARCHITECTURE.md for deep system insights
